## 🛠️ The Setup Process

We integrated the authentication flow in a Next.js App Router workspace using React 19.

### 1. Environment Configuration
To manage API credentials, we created a `.env.local` file to store our environment keys:
```env
RELIPAY_URL=https://api.relipay.dev
RELIPAY_SECRET=rp_test_your_secret_key_here
```

### 2. Dependency Installation
We installed the official SDK packages:
```bash
npm install @relipay/nextjs @relipay/react @relipay/node --legacy-peer-deps
```

